  <prompt>
    Update the `@spaarke/ui-components` top-level barrel (`src/index.ts`) to export the new `Kanban/` subpath. Bump the package version in `package.json` per Spaarke semver conventions (minor bump — new exports). Run `npm install` (or workspace equivalent) to refresh consumers.
  </prompt>

  <role>Spaarke shared-UI developer.</role>

  <goal>Barrel exports the Kanban subpath. Package version bumped. Consumers (SmartTodo, LegalWorkspace) resolve the new exports cleanly.</goal>

  <constraints>
