    <step order="2">Bump the `package.json` version (minor bump).</step>
    <step order="3">Run `npm run build` in Spaarke.UI.Components; verify clean build.</step>
    <step order="4">Run `npm install` (with the Vite-friendly flags) in consumer projects to pick up the new version.</step>
